💾 Storage Technologies
Layer	Default Dev Setup	Production Option
Metadata	JSON / SQLite (local)	PostgreSQL or MongoDB
Files	Local folder structure	AWS S3 / Google Drive
AI Logs	Local JSON	Encrypted audit log
Versioning	Timestamped snapshots	Git-style commit structure
Google Sync	Optional drive integration	OAuth-secured access

🔐 Security & Data Integrity
SHA256 hashes on saved attachments

Role-based access at object level

Proposal version locking

Agent logs are immutable

JSON schema validation before writing